            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>提醒！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%89%A9%E9%A5%AD%E8%8F%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%94%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%86%B0%E7%AE%B1%E9%87%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%89%A9%E9%A5%AD%E8%8F%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%94%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%86%B0%E7%AE%B1%E9%87%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#剩饭菜不是放到冰箱里就安全了#</span></a>】春节剩宴怎么存放才安全？①冰箱里尽量不要存放蔬菜类，肉菜可以存放，蔬菜类剩菜放时间长了容易产生亚硝酸盐；②冰箱的主要功能是防止病原微生物的快速增长，普通冰箱不能起到杀菌作用；③储存在冰箱的食品尽量在下一餐吃掉。详戳👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4861835627921511" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网快看的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/75dda851ly8hafz7zfda6j20zk0k0aeu.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/aUjO6WSglx082D3yP3LO01041200s3Ot0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674897631&amp;ssig=xgu1JzurTJ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/UQm36srTlx082D3yt0JG01041200e6p30E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674897631&amp;ssig=7ZFUH%2FnUiR&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/a9S3VlLrlx082D3yi9Og0104120096hq0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674897631&amp;ssig=rKw2RubnUI&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4861835627921511&a